flowchart LR
    Request["预测请求\nOpNode + HardwareSpec"]
    PolicyType["PolicyType"]
    Priority["PRIORITY\n默认优先级策略"]
    OOTB["OOTB_PERFORMANCE\n厂商库/实测库优先"]
    Opt["OPERATOR_OPTIMIZATION\n可解释模型优先"]
    Design["SYSTEM_DESIGN\n参数化模型优先"]
    BackendPool["Backend Pool\nLookup / TileSim / Roofline"]
    Result["SimResult"]

    Request --> PolicyType
    PolicyType --> Priority
    PolicyType -.预留.-> OOTB
    PolicyType -.预留.-> Opt
    PolicyType -.预留.-> Design
    Priority --> BackendPool
    OOTB -.-> BackendPool
    Opt -.-> BackendPool
    Design -.-> BackendPool
    BackendPool --> Result
